---
interface Props {
  founder: {
    name: string;
    role: string;
    image: string;
    linkedin: string;
    badges: string[];
  };
}
const { founder } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="team" class="relative bg-neutral-50 py-20 lg:py-32 px-6 sm:px-10 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-neutral-200"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 scroll-reveal">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-full h-full bg-yellow-400/10"></div>
          <img src={founder.image} alt={founder.name} class="relative w-full aspect-square object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:col-start-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 scroll-reveal">
          <div class="w-8 h-px bg-neutral-300"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-400">Quién está detrás</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-neutral-950 scroll-reveal" style="--d:50ms">{founder.name}</h3>
        <p class="text-yellow-600 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-2 mb-8 scroll-reveal" style="--d:100ms">{founder.role}</p>

        <div class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4 scroll-reveal" style="--d:150ms">
          <p>Ingeniero de software. CTO de Venpu (SaaS B2B para automotoras). 10+ años armando productos digitales para empresas.</p>
          <p>En Lelemon opero yo directamente. Tu contacto es conmigo, no con un account manager.</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-950 font-bold">Si me escribes directo, contesto yo: <a href="https://wa.me/56977066965" target="_blank" data-wa-cta class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-500 transition-colors underline underline-offset-4">+56 9 7706 6965</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mt-8 scroll-reveal" style="--d:200ms">
          {founder.badges.map((b) => (
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-500 bg-white border border-neutral-200 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium">{b}</span>
          ))}
          <a href={founder.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-neutral-400 hover:text-neutral-950 transition-colors font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
